rt_max`从4411到3903，显著异于正常情况。\n\n### 总结\n- **主要关注点**位于`aiops-k8s-08`节点上，多个服务异常表现与该节点上的内存可用量减少相关。\n- **建议**进行节点内存分析以及`redis-cart-0`和`currencyservice`的详细检查，以确认并解决潜在的性能瓶颈。\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_metric_keys\": [\"region_pending\", \"rrt_max\", \"node_memory_usage_rate\", \"node_memory_MemAvailable_bytes\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"aiops-k8s-05\",\n      \"reason\": \"node_memory_usage_rate and MemAvailable showed moderate decrease but no significant service anomalies from this node.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"node_memory_usage_rate decreased from 33.9% to 29.58%, median_change_ratio 0.1361; MemAvailable_bytes decreased from 8776316928 to 7296458752 bytes, p99_change_ratio 0.3448.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"aiops-k8s-08\",\n      \"reason\": \"node_memory_MemAvailable_bytes exhaustion causing multiple service latencies on this node.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"MemAvailable_bytes dropped significantly from 8776316928 to 7296458752 bytes. Services like redis-cart-0 showed rrt_max increased from 3569 to 7940, median_change_ratio 0.7596.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"redis-cart-0\",\n      \"reason\": \"Recorded significant rrt_max increase causing perceived performance issue.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"rrt_max increased from 3569 to 7940, median_change_ratio 0.7596.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"currencyservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"Experienced significant latency without node-specific anomalies.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"rrt_max showed abnormal values decreasing from 4411 to 3903.\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```"}
